# 👔 Tiebreaker Helpful

When tie vote, priority will be given to the target voted by the Tiebreaker. Note: If multiple Tiebreaker choose different tie targets at the same time, the skills of the Tiebreaker will not take effect.

  • Max
    • Set the Maximum amount of Tiebreakers that can be in a match
  • Spawn Chance
    • Set the percentage players have of getting Tiebreaker
  • Impostors can become Tiebreaker
    • ON: Impostors can become this role
    • OFF: Impostors cannot become this role
  • Crewmates can become Tiebreaker
    • ON: Crewmates can become this role
    • OFF: Crewmates cannot become this role
  • Neutrals can become Tiebreaker
    • ON: Neutrals can become this role
    • OFF: Neutrals cannot become this role
